Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.44,0:04:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.81,0:05:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.03,0:05:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to yell like that.\NI can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mingo! Stop Bellamy! He's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.93,0:05:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat, I guess you won't change your mind\Nand finish off Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.85,0:05:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.36,0:05:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Bellamy. I set you free.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you have always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.35,0:06:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are the Donquixote Family,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're Doflamingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us under your umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.37,0:06:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you! Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk to Doffy so casually,\Nyou little hoodlum!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been admiring you since I was a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.43,0:07:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us a chance! Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away, you hoodlums!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.87,0:07:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all from Nortis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.12,0:07:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a wealthy town.\NWhat's your problem with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.16,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That shitty town is boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.88,0:07:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Donquixote Family is\Nthe pride of the North Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We wanna become\Na pirate band like you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a little different from\Nthose idealistic pirates around there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you use our Jolly Roger\Nif that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.81,0:07:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you get defeated by someone,\Nyou're no longer allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure?! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't need weaklings as my subordinates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We won't get defeated! By anyone!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.91,0:08:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?! I don't think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.47,0:08:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you're the 30 million bounty,\NStraw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.69,0:08:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a delusional dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.78,0:08:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.\NThe era where pirates dream about things is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.29,0:08:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The big hidden treasure, One Piece...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.91,0:08:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots who are blinded by dream treasure don't\Nnotice the treasure around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're misled by those illusions and die.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.88,0:09:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just drivel by losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Struggle all you want;\Nthere's no escape from my Boing-Boing Fruit power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.82,0:09:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A city of gold?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.62,0:09:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sky island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The era of dreams is over,\Nyou pathetic excuses for pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I know how to throw a punch, you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.64,0:09:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I visited the Sky Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost my crew but it turned my \Nview of the world upside down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not holding a grudge against you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.01,0:10:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done picking on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you cheer me on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.09,0:10:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.63,0:10:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.49,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've changed, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.31,0:10:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, {\i1}you{\i0} have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.15,0:11:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You now use Haki that's far \Ngreater than anyone can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.25,0:11:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.88,0:11:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't push yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better stay down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Joker wants me to kill Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy's too indulgent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's giving the man who couldn't win the match\None more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy, Bellamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I thought you were gonna mess it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The assassination of Straw Hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.29,0:11:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.89,0:11:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter\Nif you can get it done or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.90,0:11:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want you to follow him about\Nso he told me to finish you off here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Young Master-{\i1}sama{\i0}'s order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? A big quake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...hope left for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.81,0:12:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me say it straight, Bellamy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your purpose was different from mine.\NFrom long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always wanted to become a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.39,0:12:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything was fine with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.44,0:12:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...destroy this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.64,0:12:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.83,0:13:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.77,0:13:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy. I set you free.\NLike you have always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.76,0:13:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellamy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but wait here.\NI'm worried about Tra-guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.81,0:13:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo and Snot are up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta get there or Tra-guy's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kick Mingo's ass for you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember this technique?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go! Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.05,0:14:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got stronger but I got stronger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.58,0:14:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This technique is far more destructive than\Nit used to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Pica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget we're fighting here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.65,0:15:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destruction Cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.16,0:15:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.37,0:15:53.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.53,0:16:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think you're serious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.09,0:16:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been beating around the bush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because we're each other's enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you say it straight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.63,0:16:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't pretend that you don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Glance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll shoot...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...through your heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.10,0:16:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said "I'll aim for your heart"...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't let go of your hand!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.44,0:16:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And "I'll keep holding your hand"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.02,0:16:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Can you keep up with me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And "Can you stick with me"!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about the positions we're in!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.22,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...need me, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vise-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here comes one more-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.32,0:17:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,100-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tenacious-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.67,0:18:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell! Ton-Ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shows no mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.17,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the warrior of Elbaph couldn't do a thing\Nagainst Vice-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good-{\i1}in{\i0}! A good foothold-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.39,0:18:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought down Hajrudin the Giant-{\i1}in{\i0}\Nand my next target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.90,0:18:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just big and not quite strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're in our way, you big shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My dream was to become\Nthe king of all Giants.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.21,0:18:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But look at me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lost in the competition.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.55,0:19:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got turned into a toy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had been saved\Nbut I still haven't paid back my debt!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How pathetic!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.23,0:19:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was willing to die to pay my debt, then...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.40,0:19:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...why am I still alive after I failed?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ton-Ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Was my gratitude...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that shallow?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I... I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.61,0:19:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go, Roronoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.94,0:19:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Destructive 1,000-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.01,0:19:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's far deeper than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry but...\Nlet me take care of that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.70,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey-{\i1}in{\i0}!\NI can't believe you're still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll make it heavier-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hellish 10,000-Ton Vise!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.74,0:20:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope there are still bones left to be crushed!\NHey-{\i1}in{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.55,0:20:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dead man can't be useful but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.01,0:20:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...if at least one of his arms still moves,\Na man can even rip off his enemy general's head.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take this! I'll give it all my life!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.81,0:21:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gungir!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use-{\i1}in{\i0}. This is 10,000 ton!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get squashed, Hajrudin!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fly away! To the kingdom of the gods!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.10,0:22:06.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.00,0:22:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Above him!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.80,0:22:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna hit the Birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.55,0:22:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Vice-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.30,0:22:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna get slashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.41,0:22:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he can't fly out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not even a bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.13,0:22:57.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.18,0:23:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you wake up, the cage will be gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sai of the Happosui Army is baffled by
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.76,0:23:15.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Baby 5 who comes on strong \Nwith her earnest feelings!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:20.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}While the both families fight fiercely to \Ndefend their pride, her sad past is revealed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the passionate man, Sai blasts\Na special secret technique which bests Don Chin Jao!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.58,0:23:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!\N"The Battle of Love! The New Leader Sai vs. Baby 5!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
